UML:TaggedValue.value: A known measure value at the location of the LR_Referent along the LR_LinearElement for the specified Linear Referencing Method. This measure value represents a new start to be used for measurements made after such location along the LR_LinearElement.

the direction used as positive for this Linear Reference Method for measurements along the base element. The default value is same with respect to the direction of the base element for positive, opposite for negative. If from and towards referents have been specified, then the value of same for positive corresponds to the direction of the towards referent.
